A)How to compile and run hymod demo with ifort in Linux
option 1) use makefile.hymod_ifort, see instructions inside the file

option 2) automatically generate batch file for compiling hymod demo
make -f makefile.hymod_ifort clean
make -f makefile.hymod_ifort -n >hymod_ifort.bat
chmod +x hymod_ifort.bat
./hymod_ifort.bat
./hymod_demo.exe

B)How to compile and run hymod demo with ifort in Windows
option 1) use hymod_ifort.bat, see instructions inside the file
option 2) use VS+IVF

C)How to compile and run hymod demo with gfortran in Linux
option 1) use makefile.hymod_gfortran, see instructions inside the file

option 2) automatically generate batch file for compiling hymod demo
make -f makefile.hymod_gfortran clean
make -f makefile.hymod_gfortran -n >hymod_gfortran.bat
chmod +x hymod_gfortran.bat
./hymod_gfortran.bat
./hymod_demo.exe

D)How to compile and run hymod demo with gfortran in Windows
option 1) use hymod_gfortran.bat, see instructions inside the file
option 2) use gfortran command prompt